<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>AdonisJS Hypermedia Starter</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A clean AdonisJS hypermedia starter with controllers, models, validators, Edge views, and test coverage."
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --page-background: #f3efe6;
        --panel-background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        --panel-border: rgba(22, 24, 35, 0.12);
        --foreground: #161823;
        --muted: #5a6072;
        --accent: #0f766e;
        --accent-strong: #115e59;
        --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(22, 24, 35, 0.12);
        --radius-xl: 32px;
        --radius-lg: 22px;
      }
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
        color: var(--foreground);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12), transparent 36%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f4ed 0%, var(--page-background) 100%);
      }
      a {
        color: inherit;
      }
      .shell {
        width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 2rem));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1.25rem 0 4rem;
      }
      .site-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
      }
      .site-header__brand a,
      .site-header__nav a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .site-header__brand {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .site-header__nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .hero {
        padding: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        background: var(--panel-background);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      }
      .hero__eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 5.4rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
      }
      .hero__body {
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .hero__actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 3rem;
        padding: 0 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .button--primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #f8fafc;
      }
      .button--primary:hover {
        background: var(--accent-strong);
      }
      .button--secondary {
        border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      }
      .feature-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }
      .feature-card {
        padding: 1.4rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
      }
      .feature-card h2 {
        margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .feature-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }
      @media (max-width: 800px) {
        .site-header {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .feature-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="shell">
      <header class="site-header">
        <div class="site-header__brand">
          <a href="/" aria-label="Home">AdonisJS Starter</a>
        </div>
        <nav class="site-header__nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <a href="https://docs.adonisjs.com">Docs</a>
          <a href="https://adocasts.com">Tutorials</a>
        </nav>
      </header>
      <main>
        <section class="hero">
          <p class="hero__eyebrow">Hypermedia starter</p>
          <h1>Build the app, not the scaffold.</h1>
          <p class="hero__body">
            This template follows the AdonisJS hypermedia starter shape with Edge
            views, resources assets, controllers, models, validators, and a clean
            Edge-rendered starting experience you can evolve into a real product.
          </p>
          <div class="hero__actions">
            <a class="button button--primary" href="https://docs.adonisjs.com">
              Read the docs
            </a>
            <a
              class="button button--secondary"
              href="https://docs.adonisjs.com/guides/concepts/deployment"
            >
              Deploy the app
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="feature-grid" aria-label="Starter highlights">
          <article class="feature-card">
            <h2>Hypermedia-first</h2>
            <p>
              Start from routes and Edge views in the same shape as the official
              hypermedia starter.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <h2>Domain-ready</h2>
            <p>
              Controllers, models, transformers, and validators already back a
              working username lifecycle.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <h2>Tested baseline</h2>
            <p>
              Unit, functional, and browser coverage stay in place while you reshape
              the starter around your product.
            </p>
          </article>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
